<p>The left aside is an <code>&lt;aside&gt;</code> element on the
  left of a
  <a href="/components/grail-layout/"><code>GrailLayout</code></a>,
  typically holding primary navigation or filters. Set
  <code>params.label</code> so assistive tech can distinguish it
  from the right aside. See the
  <a href="/components/grail-layout/">composed demo</a>.</p>
